item.title: [HIVE-20354] Semijoin hints dont work with merge statements
item.description:
When merge statement is rewritten, it ignores any comment in the query which may include hints like semijoin.
If it is, it should not be ignored.
item.summary: Semijoin hints dont work with merge statements

status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.
